I did not puree this soup. I changed a few things, I added 2 potatoes, 1 large white onion, half a red onion 3tbs of ginger, and 1 tbs of cumin for bite. Scratch the broccoli if you don't intend on making a puree, and throw in a handful of frozen peas for color. It is fabulous this way!

